{"tid":2421471,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"女團成員收「死亡威脅」含淚陷極大恐懼！經紀公司震怒喊話","createTime":"2021-02-24T13:49:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-25T11:44:32.000Z","uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"923885dfd301f0e72ebf98a7a787525ae803f940","tid":2421471,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T13:49:31.000Z","msg":"南韓女團T-ara的27歲成員朴芝妍（박지연）不單只是團中的顏值擔當，還有著超強舞蹈、歌唱實力，近年將重心放在戲劇上。不過近日她收到不明人士發出一連串死亡威脅的訊息，讓她內心受到相當大的衝擊，經紀公司透露朴芝妍本人處於相當恐懼的狀態，並且已向警方報案。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/02/24/3039733-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F02%2F24%2F3039733-PH.jpg&h=f6f9fdb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼朴芝妍外型亮眼，在女團T-ara是全方位擔當。（圖／翻攝朴芝妍IG）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/02/24/3039743-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F02%2F24%2F3039743-PH.jpg&h=8261143c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據韓媒《Sports東亞》報導，芝妍的個人Instagram、推特等社群帳號上，都收到身分不明人士發送公開的「殺害威脅」訊息，讓她陷入莫大的恐懼當中，經紀公司強硬表示會以強烈的法律手段處置。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/02/24/3039742-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F02%2F24%2F3039742-PH.jpg&h=43efcbfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲芝妍含淚收到莫大的恐懼。（圖／翻攝朴芝妍IG）<br />\n<br />\n芝妍的經紀公司「PARTNERS park」第一時間便嚴厲的發出聲明，表示為保護旗下藝人的安全，目前已報警、並請求警方進行正式調查，並強調對這次事件絕對不容忍或從輕處理，將會強硬措施進行處理。目前傳送威脅訊息的不明人士帳號已遭到停用。"},{"pid":"d825432093d0540cf2a3f8782f2755fee72347cd","tid":2421471,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T13:50:20.000Z","msg":"支持.....<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2206f35d5353476c72d8189d6fc1ee16ddb0568","tid":2421471,"uid":255310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T13:50:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae7c3abf4333f62ef54104653f53d02ce3f661dd","tid":2421471,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"d825432093d0540cf2a3f8782f2755fee72347cd","tid":2421471,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T13:50:20.000Z","msg":"支持.....<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T13:53:16.000Z","msg":"殺殺殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73655b9d0cecbdfcef62d596177b623114fecfe1","tid":2421471,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T13:53:46.000Z","msg":"會唔會有驚恐症<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c227677d3cf3983a92391158c3fe888cfff3053","tid":2421471,"uid":320204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T14:15:55.000Z","msg":"有啲驚彩瑛會收到由署名係施字頭嘅送出嘅「殺害威脅」訊息<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"269d8891eeb594c658ffa24100f3c8f23647baf8","tid":2421471,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T14:20:47.000Z","msg":"近幾日開左幾次ig live<br />\n披頭散髮素顏咁 精神幾差下"},{"pid":"a3437b88016528f4b6b090f85b204cdc1fefe2f0","tid":2421471,"uid":8795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73655b9d0cecbdfcef62d596177b623114fecfe1","tid":2421471,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T13:53:46.000Z","msg":"會唔會有驚恐症<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}